'''''Lance''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] in the service of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. At the time of the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]], it was part of the [[Defiance Task Force]], and after a brief campaign escaped the [[Anoat sector/Legends|Anoat sector]] along with the rest of the task force. It carried a cargo of thermal units, likely either bound for [[Echo Base/Legends|Echo Base]] or being evacuated from there.

Her exploits following the reconstitution of the Defiance Task Force are unknown, and it is likewise unknown whether or not the vessel participated in the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].

